# Zomato Business Performance Analysis

## Project Overview
This project analyzes global restaurant data from the Zomato dataset to understand restaurant performance across different countries, cities, cuisines, and pricing categories.

The objective of this project is to identify patterns in restaurant ratings, cost distribution, and cuisine popularity using data visualization techniques.

## Problem Statement
Restaurant aggregators and food platforms need insights into restaurant performance to better understand customer preferences, pricing trends, and regional food patterns. This project explores the Zomato dataset to uncover insights that can support data-driven decision making.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel
- DAX
- Power Query

## Key Insights
- Comparison of restaurant ratings across countries and cities
- Cost analysis of restaurants by region
- Identification of popular cuisines
- Restaurant distribution across locations

## Dataset
The dataset contains information about restaurants including:
- Restaurant name
- Location
- Cuisine
- Cost for two
- Ratings
- Country and city information

